{"tid":1301002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事)大家千祈唔好同啲長輩講信用制度!!!","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:04:37.000Z","uid":116628,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"36a78eee07b043c2ca9d7c6ebe62781a9e532982","tid":1301002,"uid":116628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"背景：呀爸之前係中港司機(無立場偏政府)，平時唔多講政治。呀媽係全職師奶，反開共產黨嘅，兩個都係以前偷渡落黎<br />\n<br />\n同已上岸退休嘅呀爸呀媽講起3年內大灣區會推信用制度，呀爸竟然出聲話：大陸行緊啦！有人冇交隧道費，結果入左黑名單，買唔到車飛，要出返黑名單就要揾律師搞一大輪！<br />\n<br />\n呀媽聽到之後勁嬲，話政府痴線，係大陸望住啲人搶劫又唔拉，依家搞埋啲咁嘅野。唔係我講都唔知有咁嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住同佢地講下吹下水，點知connect左大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好同屋企長輩講呢個信用制度，費事太多人反對，阻礙香港回歸祖國呀!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaee632b88722d8242ed8276e2b1fa4eef7ac5a3","tid":1301002,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"收到 大家記得唔好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcac7dc4c4b8bae05d3d8e5f9679837d8202f5ad","tid":1301002,"uid":8511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"「你行得正企得正, 怕乜呀?」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef44c717d8a0315078769f8631fc3170c0657b8c","tid":1301002,"uid":247981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"禁錯👎 sor<br />\n我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"21e0ac2bd086951b4a3dc7e1bf2e96778b7e5f09","tid":1301002,"uid":200136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"無 老母仍然唔擔心唔相信"},{"pid":"c3c438fee802a9a618d7b0ab1ab8bb4b22fd5bcf","tid":1301002,"uid":26562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"